response.overview: After a mobster agrees to cooperate with an FBI investigation in order to stay out of prison, he's relocated by the authorities to a life of suburban anonymity as part of a witness protection program. It's not long before a couple of his new neighbours figure out his true identity and come knocking to see if he'd be up for one more hit—suburban style.
response.tagline: In the heart of suburbia, a hit man with heart has just moved in.
response.title: The Whole Nine Yards

cast.name: Rumer Willis
cast.character: Girl Running Between Jimmy and Oz
